results.name: Number of 4-valent (or quartic) graphs with n nodes.
comment: Because the triangle A051031 is symmetric, a(n) is also the number of (n-5)-regular graphs on n vertices. - _Jason Kimberley_, Sep 22 2009
reference: R. C. Read and R. J. Wilson, An Atlas of Graphs, Oxford, 1998.
